{"tid":1600008,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國研究指全球70國以社交媒體控制輿論擔心部分國家會藉此左右民主國家選舉。","createTime":"2019-09-28T11:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T11:57:41.000Z","uid":125193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a9c05e7bd11cb1e34fb33d7f19036f2b2283aee6","tid":1600008,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T11:48:45.000Z","msg":"Now新聞台】英國有研究指出，包括中國的至少70個國家，有組織地以社交媒體控制輿論，擔心部分國家會藉此左右民主國家選舉。<br />\n<br />\n英國牛津網絡研究所發表研究報告指，全球至少70個國家的政府或政黨透過社交媒體控制輿論，國家數目較前年增加逾一倍，其中中國及俄羅斯等7個國家，更利用Facebook及Twitter等社交媒體，加強對外國的影響力。<br />\n<br />\n中國的社交媒體用戶目前是全球最多，研究所以香港近期的反修例示威為例，指內地頻頻利用社交媒體反擊，而示威亦成為中國操控社交媒體的催化劑。<br />\n<br />\n社交媒體的影響力近年愈來愈大，網上輿論足以左右國家或地區選舉選情。報告指26個專制國家政府會控制網上輿論，打壓民意和新聞自由，多達45個民主國家的政府或政黨，都會利用類似方式控制輿論，亦會用假帳戶增加社交媒體上的追蹤數量。<br />\n<br />\n報告認為，這是因為政治人物需要利用網絡宣傳，贏取公眾支持。<br />\n<br />\n有研究人員指出，國家大規模控制社交媒體輿論的現象愈來愈嚴重，對民主制度亦構成很大威脅，又指中國及俄羅斯都各自有一套操控輿論的方式，憂慮中國往後，會開始以社交媒體干預其他民主國家選舉，包括加拿大下月的大選及明年美國總統選戰。<br />\n<br />\n面對愈來愈多社交媒體的虛假內容，英國及法國在內的20個國家日前在聯合國大會中簽署協議，制止在網絡散播假新聞，而Twitter在較早時亦封鎖來自世界各地數以千計，涉及散播假訊息的假帳戶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=364394&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D364394%26refer%3DShare&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8rxmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=6a3f5daa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D364394%26refer%3DShare&h=0f0d0fe6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=364394&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"ec100da74e4c9a1f3e5f0441a0cd75086ba04230","tid":1600008,"uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T11:49:27.000Z","msg":"終於識驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太遲了"},{"pid":"abd5cb119b6a9c9351a927fd899aae824358e9c0","tid":1600008,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T11:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哈哈"},{"pid":"9fe8fb1460cd768659e179019342c77c78a7644e","tid":1600008,"uid":296677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T11:53:48.000Z","msg":"訓咗既人唔會醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9980f5f8490b3c32b69ef24fe2b59e091b4d6e1c","tid":1600008,"uid":197404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T11:54:44.000Z","msg":"咪住先<br />\n中國都唔係民主國家"},{"pid":"b571fbf9d3eebbb1c7ae6115a9845c96f534364b","tid":1600008,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T11:56:22.000Z","msg":"而家先走出嚟鳩噏兩句收尾刀<br />\n同迖哥一直關注冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bf9ab715143c42b4bac6e4fc477c967e713601","tid":1600008,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T11:57:18.000Z","msg":"chinazi"},{"pid":"4992935a0140b5d844884418877a7d9c55b5d362","tid":1600008,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b571fbf9d3eebbb1c7ae6115a9845c96f534364b","tid":1600008,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T11:56:22.000Z","msg":"而家先走出嚟鳩噏兩句收尾刀<br />\n同迖哥一直關注冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T11:57:24.000Z","msg":"人地叫達狗"},{"pid":"7962ed9baf9a5daae72537cabc8782ee17283549","tid":1600008,"uid":264121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T11:57:41.000Z","msg":"咁又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日落帝國都唔做野架啦"}]}